{"tid":846218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台「地空演練」應對解放軍","createTime":"2018-10-03T09:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T10:24:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35b0a069f47e410ca5fe02492eb19323019c4082","tid":846218,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181003/20513269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513269&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=3f6ff99e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513269&h=aa4bf7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181003/20513269</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月03日 <br />\n<br />\n台「地空演練」應對解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181003/large/a1704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181003%2Flarge%2Fa1704a.gif&h=0c5cea33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣將舉行地空作戰操練；圖為眼鏡蛇直升機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為強化台海防衞、應對解放軍威脅，台軍延續「實戰仿真」方向，計劃明年起恢復每季一次的「戰備月」。因應2019年戰備月，台第三作戰區將在日內動員精銳部隊，在桃園市龍潭舉行「地空整體作戰」實兵操演，出動戰機、各類型直升機與地面部隊共同執行地空聯合作戰。<br />\n<br />\n據報，這次實兵操演是依據台灣總統蔡英文提出「濱海決勝、灘岸殲敵」的作戰構想。國防部已邀請蔡親自校閱，但仍待總統府確認行程後再決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擬恢復每季一次「戰備月」<br />\n<br />\n台灣政府力推戰力提升，國防部長嚴德發要求三軍針對戰備演訓精進，今年重新提出自1991年暫停實施的戰備月，加強聯合戰鬥的思維。估計明年起台軍各作戰區每季度舉行一次。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n陷入新冷戰　隨時擦槍走火<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n劉霞訪余英時　擬明年赴台辦攝影展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普阻華「佔領」南海<br />\n<br />\n陷入新冷戰　隨時擦槍走火<br />\n<br />\n貿戰火頭燒到南海中美軍艦相距41米險撞"},{"pid":"71d7010f76bcb94852a17d99d3b1e3bdbe3ee18e","tid":846218,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"台軍整肅左堆共碟後應該露以頂到三個月...否則三日"},{"pid":"6c60db6c1af12839169c8b1f8ff0ed1db3dc7810","tid":846218,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"WW3 is coming<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876d31c65f73c3ce7fe4ac9d72fd7be459f987b9","tid":846218,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6e6959a02ec272bcf2b615f81b3647794e643f","tid":846218,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁樣算點先<br />\n<br />\n連比我搶既機會都無"}]}